Package: PGRealEstate
Type: Package
Title: Hedonic and Multilateral Index Methods for Real Estate Price Comparison
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Farley Ishaak, Pim Ouwehand, Mohammed Kardal, Vivek Gajadhar, 
    Odens van der Zwan, David Pietersz, Liu Nuo Su, Cynthia Cao
Maintainer: Farley Ishaak <ff.ishaak@cbs.nl>
Description: Provides functions to compute price indices using various hedonic and
    multilateral methods, including Laspeyres, Paasche, Fisher, and HMTS (Hedonic
    Multilateral Time series re-estimation with splicing). The central function
    calculate_method_index() offers a unified interface for running these methods
    on structured datasets. This package is designed to support index construction
    workflows for real estate and other domains where quality-adjusted price
    comparisons over time are essential.
